Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:09.64,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1870,530)\fad(200,200)\frz-90\fsp4.5\blur5}いつからなんだろう強くなったね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:16.73,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1870,530)\fad(200,200)\frz-90\fsp4.5\blur5}広い世界探したものは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:24.44,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1870,530)\fad(200,200)\frz-90\fsp4.5\blur5}旅路の果てにきっと見つかるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:37.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}依旧波涛汹涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:44.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说 你吃什么才会变成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:47.13,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么...其实也没吃什么特别的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:49.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蠢货...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:54.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}哎 这么样才能变大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\blur5}不能这么干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\blur5}这不是人干的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}本大爷可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}只要达到目的 就算失去做人的资格也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:02.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}就算化为恶鬼 本大爷都照做不误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}有必要说得这样夸张吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:06.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}明明只要学会自重一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.26,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}自重？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:08.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}本大爷没听过这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}至少本大爷的字典里没这个词儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.86,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:15.40,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露的胸真大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.00,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且形状也好可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.86,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可 可爱...？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:20.63,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我稍微摸一摸也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}哈尔希洛 根本不用忍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:29.40,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就摸一下下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你早已败在自己的本能之下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}不然 你早就强行拉着我离开 大喊出声了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那里 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.93,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就觉得手感肯定会很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}这样啊...我输了...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}我输了吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:50.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}我们啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你这个笨蛋 我们其实...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:53.36,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}并没有输啊...我们赢了的...！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.43,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我再多摸一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.26,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你...说什么...？？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.76,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要 那样子摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:59.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}这是我们的本能...我们的思想上的胜利...！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:01.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}这怎么会是我们的失败呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:07.16,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉就像小婴儿一样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}不！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}是胜利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}我有说错什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.20,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好赞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}原来是我们的胜利吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}不知不觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}就赢了吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}哎...说实在的 好在意啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}虽然并没有看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}还没到头盔的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:30.13,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这里聚集着我们的梦想...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁着这难得的时机...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:37.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们感受到活着是什么样的滋味...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 让梦的剧场拉开帷幕吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿这样子好像很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿总这样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.06,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我倒觉得梦儿很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.06,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？才没有那样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿哪里比较可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:38.80,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿不像我这么胖 看起来还软软的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:42.46,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 我觉得席赫露不胖的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.33,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梦儿的那种柔软的感觉 看起来很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:52.23,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}诶嘿嘿 好吃的什么的 梦儿可不是食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:56.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有点刺激过头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完了完了完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这两个人到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脑海中浮现的场景太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:21.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(45,45)\fs40\alpha&H82&\3c&H0085FF&\blur5}由于这段没找到中文翻译\N而且作者不会日文\N只好对着英语翻译\N实在对不住啦（渣渣英语）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.50,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Want to take a bite? Maybe around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.30,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.56,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Maybe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.73,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.26,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Come on, don't hold back~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}B-but it will hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.33,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}（Now, now, over here!）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.50,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能咬这里一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.30,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...我不能..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.56,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那里可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.73,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.26,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来嘛~不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但..但是那里会很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.33,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}（来吧 来吧 我来了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...我不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.46,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放开我 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.46,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你叫我混蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你难道不想看么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想就这样放弃么 这难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的咽得下这口气不后悔么 哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能会后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能保证绝不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:49.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是继续这样下去又怎么样 事情又会如何发展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会如何发展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在的我们如此亢奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}继续这样下去就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会陷入无法挽回的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我们要回到房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:04.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的房间 四个男人的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种事 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我绝不能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:28.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我们所有人的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:35.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无法恋爱的感情 所有的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:39.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部被天空 和天空中的繁星带走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空中的那轮红月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:50.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一次见到时不可思议的那轮红月 依旧挂在天空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:55.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}依旧是那么遥远 那么深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美丽的夜空中 零落闪烁着的星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仿佛将要坠落一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的灵魂在索求着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:11.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}某个远方无可替代的东西\N这个美妙世界的地平线 一定也在渴求着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.20,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下雨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得找个地方躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫古索已经有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}觉悟过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能放手做出这种事么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 做不出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能放手去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让天都为之颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神也在聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此 就前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向前冲 沿着这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫古索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:38.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们现在真正的感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}误 误会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么误会？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你个死色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 露天浴耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德你这个白痴 恶心 色鬼 死变态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:30.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有多远滚多远 永远不要回来
